Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:22.18,Song1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}覺醒吧 RETURNER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:23.77,Song1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}誠心冀望就行了
